## ğŸ“– Project Overview

In this activity, I analyzed DNS and ICMP traffic in transit using data captured from a network protocol analyzer tool. The goal was to identify the network protocol affected during the cybersecurity incident and document findings in a professional report.

Knowing how to identify potentially malicious or problematic traffic on a network helps cybersecurity analysts assess security risks and reinforce network security.

